  "title": "7mths Medical Technologist - Up to $2.8K #HKH",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties and Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Involve in daily routine lab operations including specimen collection, processing and data recording</li><li>Operate equipment and perform appropriate quality control, calibration, and troubleshooting</li><li>Attend to request for information (e.g specimen information, lab results and/or materials (e.g blood tubes, slides, blocks)</li><li>Maintenance of lab equipment and support research, education and innovation when applicable</li><li>Ensure compliance in safety, care and other applicable regulatory requirements of Lab</li><li>Assist in clinical practice improvement activities if required</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p>•\tMin Diploma in Biomedical Science or equivalent<br />•\tSome working experience / internship is preferred </p><p><strong>Office hours, Mon to Fri </strong><br /><strong>Up to $2.8K</strong><br /><br />Interested candidates, please forward your resume to <strong>kevynhuang@recruitexpress.com.sg </strong></p><p>Consultant: Huang Jingsheng Kevyn (R1333338) <br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599) </p>",
